title: HPE stock sinks 9% on revenue miss and weak server numbers
description: CFO Marie Myers said server revenue was hit by the timing of AI service shipments and lower-than-expected government spending.
content:
Hewlett Packard Enterprise shares fell 5% Friday after the company reported fourth-quarter revenue that missed analyst expectations.
